%N A016221 Inverse of 2212th cyclotomic polynomial.
%C A016221 Periodic with period length 2212. - _Ray Chandler_, Apr 07 2017
%H A016221 Ray Chandler, <a href="/A016221/b016221.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..3000</a>
%H A016221 <a href="/index/Per#periodic">Index entries for periodic sequences</a>, period 2212.
